Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' that are directly followed by 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress' occurring before 'Completed + In Call' in the same case
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Percentage of all activity executions in the log that correspond to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all cases

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + In Progress' appears in variants that eventually lead to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + In Progress' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + In Call' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' occurrences that do not transition to any 'Wait' state (e.g., 'Accepted + Wait - User', 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor', etc.)
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all cases where 'Accepted + Wait - User' does not happen

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress' as the first activity in a case
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of variants containing 'Accepted + In Progress' that include at least one occurrence of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Ratio of the frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress' to the frequency of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + In Progress' is repeated consecutively within the same case
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + In Progress' activities

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' activities that are followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases that end with 'Completed + Closed' versus those that end with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Percentage of all 'Completed + In Call' events that are immediately preceded by 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: Percentage of 'Completed + In Call' out of all 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average number of 'Accepted + In Progress' occurrences per case in variants that contain 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' that transition directly to 'Completed + Resolved' without intermediate waiting or queuing states
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Number of variants where 'Accepted + In Progress' appears more than twice before reaching 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + In Progress' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + In Call' occurs

Name: Percentage of total process execution time spent in 'Accepted + In Progress' states across all cases
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress' appearing after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' compared to its frequency appearing as the initial activity
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Percentage of cases where 'Accepted + In Progress' occurs but 'Completed + In Call' never occurs
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all cases where 'Completed + In Call' does not happen

Name: Ratio of variants starting with 'Accepted + In Progress' versus those starting with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' that result in 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + In Progress' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Metric: Number of 'Accepted + In Progress' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + In Call' occurs
